<title>Himak onnahinli hoka ƲIT91</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Himak onnahinli hoka,
 Sai okcha̱ya hokʋt,
 Ʋba isht taloa 'chukma
 Taloa la chi̱shke.

[V2]
 Achukma sa nusi kak osh
 Ʋm ʋlhpiesʋshke;
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla kak o̱,
 Sai okcha̱ya hoke.

[V3]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla hoka,
 Himak a fehna ka,
 Pit ahninchit, holitoblit,
 Im antia lashke.

[V4]
 Si yʋmohmi pulla hocha,
 Nitak moma hoka,
 Anukfihinli li hokʋt
 Shoyohbi beka chi̱.

[V5]
 Chisʋs sai Okchalinchi ma!
 Si apelakbano,
 Aiahnit chi hoho̱yo hosh
 Taloho̱wa lishke.</lyrics>
<aka>Morning Hymn</aka>
<hymn_number>91</hymn_number>
</song>